===Proper noun===
'''tricolpates''' (plural only) 

# {{botany}} in the APG system a name for one of the major clades, comprising most of the former [[dicotyledon]]s.  This group has [[tricolpate pollen]] or a type derived from this.  Not in use in the singular: [[tricolpate]] is an adjective.

